quran[14{c,v,t}:
109,1,keh do ke ae kafroo
109,2,mein unn ki ibadat nahi karta jin ki ibadat tum karte ho
109,3,aur nah tum uss ki ibadat karne walay ho jis ki ibadat mein karta hon
109,4,aur nah mein unn ki ibadat karne wala hon jin ki ibadat tum ne ki hai
109,5,aur nah tum uss ki ibadat karne walay ho jis ki ibadat mein karta hon
109,6,tumahray liye tumhara deen hai aur mere liye mera deen
110,1,jab Allah ki madad aa jaye aur fatah naseeb ho jaye
110,2,aur ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum dekh lau ke log fouj Dur fouj Allah ke deen mein daakhil ho rahay hain
110,3,"to apne Rab ki hamd ke sath uss ki tasbeeh karo, aur uss se mughfirat ki dua mango, be shak woh bara tauba qubool karne wala hai"
111,1,toot gay abu lahab ke haath aur namuraad ho gaya woh
111,2,uss ka maal aur jo kuch is ne kamaya woh uss ke kisi kaam nah aaya
111,3,zaroor woh shola zan aag mein dala jaye ga
111,4,"aur ( uss ke sath ) uss ki joru bhi, lagai bujhai karne wali"
111,5,uss ki gardan mein monjh ki rassi hogi
